<pre class="prettyprint lang-cs">代码示例：
        public static double JieCheng(int number)
        {
            if (number == 0)
            {
                return 0;
            }

            //初始值必须设置为1
            double result = 1; 

            for (int i = number; i &gt;= 1; i--)
            {
                result = result*i;
            }
            return result;
        }</pre>